%% Diagram: Configuration Management SPA — async apply-status UX (AD-034)
%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {
  'primaryColor': '#4f46e5', 'primaryTextColor': '#ffffff',
  'primaryBorderColor': '#3730a3', 'lineColor': '#94a3b8',
  'secondaryColor': '#10b981', 'tertiaryColor': '#f59e0b',
  'background': '#ffffff', 'mainBkg': '#f8fafc',
  'nodeBorder': '#cbd5e1', 'clusterBkg': '#f1f5f9',
  'clusterBorder': '#e2e8f0', 'titleColor': '#1e293b',
  'edgeLabelBackground': '#ffffff', 'textColor': '#334155'
}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant S as Config screen
    participant M as useMutation (TanStack)
    participant C as apiClient
    participant API as Control-plane API
    participant AS as useApplyStatus
    participant FB as Toast / StatusBadge

    U->>S: Submit create / edit / delete
    S->>M: mutate(payload)
    M->>C: POST / PATCH / DELETE /services...
    C->>API: request (credentials: include)
    alt 422 validation / domain rejection
        API-->>C: 4xx {detail}
        C-->>M: ApiError(detail)
        M-->>S: inline field / toast error
    else 202 accepted
        API-->>C: 202 {apply_status, version, active_version}
        C-->>M: ApplyMutationResponse
        M->>S: invalidate queries (list refresh)
        M->>FB: toast "Change queued — applying…"
        S->>AS: enable poll(serviceId)
        loop every 1s while pending | queued | applying
            AS->>C: GET /services/{id}/apply-status
            C->>API: request
            API-->>AS: ApplyStatusView
            AS->>FB: StatusBadge = current state
        end
        alt reaches active
            AS->>FB: success toast + active badge
        else reaches failed
            AS->>FB: error toast + last_error + still-live active_version
        else 30s soft-timeout
            AS->>FB: "taking longer than expected" (slow 5s poll)
        end
    end
